     H            Y.
     FFCEIN   IF  E           K        DISK
     F            FCEPP011                          KRENAMEFCEPP01X
     FFCEOUT  O   E                    DISK                      A
     C*****************************************************
     IFCEPP01X
     I              A2KIKI                          XXKIKI
     I              A2TUSZ                          XXTUSZ
     I              A2KUBI                          XXKUBI
     C*****************************************************
     C                     READ FCEPP01X                 90
     C           *IN90     DOWEQ'0'
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     A2KIKI
     C           XXKIKI    IFNE *BLANK
     C                     MOVELXXKIKI    A2KIKI
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     Z-ADDXXTUSZ    A2TUSZ
     C                     Z-ADDXXKUBI    A2KUBI
     C                     WRITEFCEPP011
     C                     READ FCEPP01X                 90
     C                     ENDDO
     C*
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
     C*
